column2: Yeh Kahani Hai Diya Aur Toofan Ki
Hansne Ki Chah Ne Kitna Mujhe
Kya Hawa Chali Baba Ritu Badli
Kaun Aaya Mere Mann Ke Dware
Apne Liye Jiye To Kya Jiye
Har Taraf Ab Yehi Afsane Hain
Hai Jag Mein Jiska Naam Amar
Kaal Ka Pahiya Ram Krishna Hari
Ae Bhai Zara Dekh Ke Chalo
Lapak Jhapak Tu Aa Re Badarwa
Meri Bhains Ko Danda Kyon Mara
Jab Pyar Kiya To Marna Kyun
Yeh Natak Kavi Likh Gaye Kalidas
Ae Dost Mere Maine Duniya Dekhi Hai
Taqat Watan Ki Hum Se Hai
Mud Mud Ke Na Dekh Mud Mud Ke
Chandi Ka Badan Sone Ki Nazar
Na To Caravan Ki Talash Hai
Dukh Bhare Din Beete Re Bhaiya
Umadh Ghumadh Kar Aai Re Ghata
Ham Bhi Hain Tum Bhi Ho
Logon Ki Zuban Pe Apna Naam
